trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class represents the type on which the XML Web service is based.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> representa o tipo no qual o serviço Web XML se baseia.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> on which this XML Web service is based.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Type" /> na qual esse serviço Web XML é baseado.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols" /> value that specifies the transmission protocols that are used to decrypt data sent in the XML Web service request.
trans-unit.target: Um valor <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols" /> que especifica o protocolo de transmissão usado para descriptografar os dados enviados na solicitação de serviço Web XML.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" />.

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
trans-unit.target: A chave associada à duplicata <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> desejada.

trans-unit.source: Returns the duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a duplicata <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associada à chave especificada.

trans-unit.source: The duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: A duplicata <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associada à chave especificada.

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
Returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: Retorna o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associado à chave especificada.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> que indica se as transmissões de dados SOAP enviadas para esse serviço Web XML e recebidas dele são codificadas por padrão.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se as transmissões de dados SOAP enviadas e recebidas esse serviço da Web em XML são codificadas por padrão. Caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um <see cref="T:System.String" /> que contém o namespace ao qual este serviço Web XML pertence.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.String" /> que contém o namespace ao qual pertence este serviço da Web em XML.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> que indica se as mensagens SOAP que são roteadas para esse serviço Web XML são roteadas com base no cabeçalho HTTP <see langword="SOAPAction" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> Se as mensagens SOAP que são roteadas para esse serviço da Web em XML são roteadas com base no <see langword="SOAPAction" /> cabeçalho HTTP; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.
